structured.title: User Reacts To New Device Setup
structured.overview: The user comments that they have spent about fifteen minutes learning how to set up a new item or device, decides to leave it as is and move on to other tasks, and expresses relief and satisfaction with how it looks. They then ask their partner for an opinion on it.

transcript_segments.text: Yes. Indeed. Well, spent fifteen minutes now just learning how to set it all up, and I'm gonna leave it and get on with stuff now.
transcript_segments.speaker: SPEAKER_0
